Preconditions:
The `words` array should not be null.
The `order` string should not be null.
The `words` array should contain at least one word.
The `order` string should contain all the characters of the alien alphabet.
The `order` string should not contain any duplicate characters.

Postconditions:
The method should return `true` if the `words` array is sorted lexicographically according to the given `order` of the alphabet.
The method should return `false` if the `words` array is not sorted lexicographically according to the given `order` of the alphabet.